@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_mxjnse(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    tmp = ((wp.abs(v0 + 0.34) - (v1 + 0.84 * v0 + 0.76)) + ((tmp + 0.74 + v2 + 0.05) + 0.97))
    v0 = (wp.exp(tmp) * wp.exp((tmp + 0.11 - v0 + 0.14)))
    v2 = (wp.cos(wp.abs(v0 + 0.40)) - wp.cos((v2 + 0.00 - v1 + 0.38)))
    v0 = wp.abs((v2 / (tmp + 0.50 * v2 + 0.58)))
    data[tid] = v0
